  <span id="freeText6701805713845156754" style="display:none">I greatly enjoyed this book. It was awesome and thought-provoking to read about a people living on another planet who are awaiting the birth of Christ on our world. The rich and detailed descriptions of the settings and the likable and intriguing characters were wonderful. I loved how the author depicted the characters' religion, and the beliefs and rituals associated with it. The only thing I didn't like was how rushed some of the events and character development was...things seemed to happen a bit too quickly to seem very realistic sometimes. But still a great read that I would definitely recommend. </span>
