    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer407944065" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer11661138010928896601">Great read. Did not have many characters which made the book flow very smoothly and easy to follow. I would recommend this book to individuals who love action, compassion, and purpose. Christianity was present throughout the book which gave it a gentle message about what God would do if you trust and believe in Him. I could not put the book down, especially at the very end.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


